{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Code your way to glory</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Control your heroes using the <strong>C#</strong> programming language, and unleash them into a massive <strong>seamless</strong> world. Your bots will <strong>hack and slash</strong> their way through hordes of Orks, level up, craft weapons for the Dwarfs, disregard Elves, acquire gold, brew <i><strong>colorful</strong></i> mushrooms and gaze into the Abyss. All this while you can sit back, <i>relax</i>, fine-tune your code and admire your bots' progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This game is made for you</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Be a <i>Hero</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Learn the forgotten art of C#, a programming language, used to develop this game, to create your own bots.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Loot, loot, <strong>loot</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Play as any of the archetypical classes including healer, tank, and damage dealer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Let the game play itself.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore Gothic Horror world inspired by the classics of High Fantasy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Kill everyone.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2647960?t=1736485537","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647960/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1736485537","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647960/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736485537","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647960/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736485537","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2